    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly in incredible shape! I have taken such good care of it, and it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and looks absolutely stunning inside and out. I'm really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be so happy with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
